description: Welcome to 22 Liberty Drive Premier Luxury waterfront residences.This stunning corner residence features floor to ceiling windows with a beautiful Chef’s kitchen with custom high gloss white lacquer cabinetry, state-of the art-appliances Wolf stove & wall oven, Miele, Subzero and wine chiller.Spacious living/dining room that leads to a large private balcony with great Seaport views.The primary suite boasts a luxurious bathroom gorgeous marble soaking tub,glass enclosed shower,double vanity, customized walk-in closet.Spacious second bedroom features custom closet.2nd full size bath.Additional features include large custom coat/utility closet,custom electric window shades and direct access to 1 car garage deeded parking.Extra storage space comes with the unit.Resident amenities include 24 hour concierge/doorman,fitness center,residents lounge with private waterfront terrace over looking the harbor.Located to Seaport District's finest restaurants,shops,cafes,habor walk, Airport.
